<div class='otherEdition' id='edition_32905382'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/32905382-the-unwomanly-face-of-war"><img alt="The Unwomanly Face of War: An Oral History of Women in World War II" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1481621902i/32905382._UY200_.jpg" />
