<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/39278860-dimitri-liakhovitski"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/39278860-dimitri-liakhovitski">Dimitri Liakhovitski</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Is the translation really so bad? &quot;Liaisons&quot;? What is actually meant is: the &quot;wireman&quot; (or, in this case - wirewoman), commo woman.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Is the translation really so bad? "Liaisons"? What is actually meant is: the "wireman" (or, in this case - wirewoman), commo woman.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
