<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/19003531.Svetlana_Alexievich"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1612787420p3/19003531.jpg);'></div>
